.:: Puzzle 4x7-Level-2-1::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: puzzles, dancing, fishing, video-games, drawing, camping, sudoku
7 different brands of cigars are smoked: davidoff, vegafina, baccarat, swisher, dunhill, cain, game
There are 7 different favourite colors: azure, black, light-blue, yellow, white, chestnut, purple
7 different pets are kept: ferret, fish, goldfish, guinea-pig, mouse, rat, lizard
 1. the person who likes yellow is on the far right##1
 2. the person who likes white is the swisher-smoker##1
 3. the owner of the mouse is the person who likes light-blue##1
 4. the vegafina-smoker is on the left of the owner of the rat##1
 5. the davidoff-smoker is on the right of the game-smoker##1
 6. the person who's hobby is dancing is the person who likes light-blue##1
 7. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the dunhill-smoker##1
 8. the owner of the guinea-pig is between the owner of the lizard and the cain-smoker##2
 9. the dunhill-smoker is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
10. the person who's hobby is fishing is in the middle##1
11. the person who likes azure is the person who's hobby is drawing##1
12. the person who's hobby is drawing is the owner of the ferret##1
13. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left of the baccarat-smoker##1
14. the cain-smoker is the owner of the goldfish##1
15. the owner of the rat is on the left of the game-smoker##1
16. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left of the person who's hobby is camping##1
17. the person who likes chestnut is on the left of the baccarat-smoker##1
18. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the right of the dunhill-smoker##1
19. the person who likes purple is on the right of the owner of the fish##1

.:: Answer ::.
